tHk7d", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 21, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8490269, "raw_content": "The SAVE America Act stands for the Safeguard American Voter Eligibility Act. It\u2019s a federal elections bill focused on requiring proof of U.S. citizenship and photo ID for voting. \n\n\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f Full Meaning\n\nS- Safeguard  \nA- American  \nV- Voter  \nE- Eligibility  \nAct\n\n\ud83d\udccc What the name implies\n- The bill\u2019s stated purpose is to \u201csafeguard\u201d federal elections by ensuring only U.S. citizens can register and vote.  \n- It does this by requiring in\u2011person documentary proof of citizenship to register and photo ID to cast a ballot. \n\nIf you want, I can also break down what counts as \u201cproof of citizenship,\u201d how this would change voting in Colorado, or why the bill is politically contentious right now.\n\n#LiveTheRevelation ", "author": "SovereignSon", "created": 1773588132880, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "SAVE American Act", "last_comment_created": 1773588132879, "content": "<p>The SAVE America Act stands for the Safeguard American Voter Eligibility Act. It\u2019s a federal elections bill focused on requiring proof of U.S. citizenship and photo ID for voting.</p>\n<p>\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f Full Meaning</p>\n<p>S- Safeguard<br />\nA- American<br />\nV- Voter<br />\nE- Eligibility<br />\nAct</p>\n<p>\ud83d\udccc What the name implies</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The bill\u2019s stated purpose is to \u201csafeguard\u201d federal elections by ensuring only U.S. citizens can register and vote.</li>\n<li>It does this by requiring in\u2011person documentary proof of citizenship to register and photo ID to cast a ballot.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you want, I can also break down what counts as \u201cproof of citizenship,\u201d how this would change voting in Colorado, or why the bill is politically contentious right now.</p>\n<p>#LiveTheRevelation</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 21, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2032998404897517962", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASGItHSfm", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 29, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8490106, "raw_content": "", "author": "KuzoKevin", "created": 1773581742820, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Finnigantoflannigan", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASGItHSfm.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/JakeCan72/status/2032998404897517962", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "As my great grandmother from Queens used to say -\"Go scratch your ass with a broken milk bottle.\"", "last_comment_created": 1773584029525, "content": "", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 30, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 108, "created": 1773539565000, "id": "2032998404897517962", "video": {"preview": "